{"tid":859604,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會跟聲優去揀動畫睇? 例如有d聲優配親都係d幾good既","createTime":"2018-10-12T15:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T12:49:59.000Z","uid":6327,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"27ad6d74517c3243a94f7c8342dba788ee65a090","tid":859604,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"我想講既例子係花澤香菜 <br />\n<br />\n我發覺佢配親都有好好既發揮 <br />\n原來今年睇到喊死人果兩套比宇宙更遠的地方同命運石之門zero都係佢有份配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劇情原來都唔差 點會咁巧合<br />\n原來睇翻呢幾年命運石之門 三月的獅子 絕園暴風雨 PSYCHO-PASS同埋言葉之庭都係佢擔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家不妨可以睇多小小呢位聲優配既動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tZaMcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tZaMcb.jpg&h=46fb0447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ac93ea49f346624c0f665a7aaebdb1cbed0301b","tid":859604,"uid":15954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"打手"},{"pid":"8d3bf3261c5f20a5e8910efa3f7def52f56d8733","tid":859604,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"萩原聖人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢個其實唔算聲優<br />\n<br />\n只係佢配得都幾好睇"},{"pid":"b0558010cc2355b88e12547d8462ccd9864a3585","tid":859604,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ac93ea49f346624c0f665a7aaebdb1cbed0301b","tid":859604,"uid":15954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:59:08.000Z","msg":"高質係要分享既"},{"pid":"eb06b657c28b23e3e6651d2a7f12453c5d9f307b","tid":859604,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T